name: SOFTENER LIQUID FABRIC CLO SOFT 1 GAL
description: Fabric Softner. Enhances the softness and finish of linens and clothing. Delightfully fresh scent leaves linens and clothing with a fresh, just-washed fragrance. Eliminates static cling and reduces wrinkles. Safe for use on all washable linen and clothing--use in commercial, home style and high efficiency (HE) machines. Works well in all water conditions and temperatures.

name: DETERGENT LAUNDRY POWDER BLUE WAM 40 LB
description: Powdered Laundry Detergent. Cleans, whitens and leaves a fresh lemon scent. Safe for all types of no iron polyester/cotton fabrics. Great for hard water--built-in water softener prevents over-sudsing. Dilutions: Light soil, 1/2 cup per load; medium soil, 3/4 cup per load; heavy soil, 1 cup per load. Provides excellent soils suspensions, penetrates deed soil stains, and rinses easily even in cool water. For automatic institutional machines, follow manufacturer's recommended use instructions.

name: DETERGENT LAUNDRY LIQUID WAM 1 GAL
description: Laundry Detergent. Quickly dissolves stubborn, greasy and oily stains. Can be used as a presoak on heavy soils. Safe for all washable fabrics, works in all temperatures. White with a fresh clean scent. For use with low water temperatures. Dilution ratio: 1/2 cup to 50 lbs of laundry.
